This is for
<a href=\"https://github.com/lbl-srg/modelica-buildings/issues/557\">issue 557</a>.
</li>
<li>
April 2, 2011 by Michael Wetter:<br/>
Added <code>homotopy</code> operator.
</li>
<li>
March 10 2010, by Michael Wetter:<br/>
First implementation.
</li>
</ul>
</html>"));
end Interior;
